full_description:
Visit SIL – The leading Real Estate Show in Portugal !
At FIL, Lisbon - Parque das Nações.
A Lounge where you can buy, sell or rent a home, vacation home, office, commercial space or other real estate assets.
If you want to invest, obtain financing or any other service associated with the real estate sector, visit SIL, a meeting point for investors, entrepreneurs, technicians, public bodies and potential buyers.
In Exhibition:
SIL Cities (municipalities),
Real Estate Promotion;
Real Estate Mediation;
Banking;
Residential Tourism;
Trade and Services;
Construction, Rehabilitation and Sustainability;
Architecture;
Official Entities .
Conferences – see program www.imobiliario.fil.pt
Focusing on the past, present and future of cities, the business plan for sustainable cities,  among others.
Tickets on sale at https://tickets.fil.pt/
